data.title: Cochylimorpha
data.text:
Genus of tortrix moths

Cochylimorpha Cochylimorpha alternana Scientific classification Domain: Eukaryota Kingdom: Animalia Phylum: Arthropoda Class: Insecta Order: Lepidoptera Family: Tortricidae Tribe: Cochylini Genus: Cochylimorpha

Razowski, 1959 Type species Cochylis faviliana

Staudinger, 1859.

Cochylimorpha is a genus of moths of the family Tortricidae.[1]
